label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on the aldehyde or oxo group of donors, NAD or NADP as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which an aldehyde or ketone (oxo) group acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces NAD or NADP.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on the CH-CH group of donors

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which a CH-CH group acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces a hydrogen or electron acceptor.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on the CH-NH2 group of donors

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which a CH-NH2 group acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces a hydrogen or electron acceptor.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on the CH-NH2 group of donors, NAD or NADP as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which a CH-NH2 group acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces NAD+ or NADP.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on the CH-NH2 group of donors, oxygen as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which a CH-NH2 group acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces an oxygen molecule.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on the CH-NH group of donors

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which a CH-NH group acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces a hydrogen or electron acceptor.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on the CH-NH group of donors, NAD or NADP as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which a CH-NH group acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces NAD or NADP.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on NAD(P)H

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which NADH or NADPH acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces a hydrogen or electron acceptor.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on NAD(P)H, heme protein as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which NADH or NADPH acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces a heme protein.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on NAD(P)H, quinone or similar compound as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which NADH or NADPH acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces a quinone or a similar acceptor molecule.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on a sulfur group of donors

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which a sulfur-containing group acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces a hydrogen or electron acceptor.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on a sulfur group of donors, NAD(P) as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which a sulfur-containing group acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces NAD or NADP.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on a sulfur group of donors, quinone or similar compound as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which a sulfur-containing group acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces quinone or a related compound.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on a heme group of donors

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which a heme group acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces a hydrogen or electron acceptor.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on diphenols and related substances as donors

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which a diphenol or related substance acts as a hydrogen or electron donor and reduces a hydrogen or electron acceptor.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on peroxide as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which the peroxide group acts as a hydrogen or electron acceptor.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on paired donors, with incorporation or reduction of molecular oxygen

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which hydrogen or electrons are transferred from each of two donors, and molecular oxygen is reduced or incorporated into a donor.

label.value: 2-oxoglutarate-dependent dioxygenase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the reaction: A + 2-oxoglutarate + O2 = B + succinate + CO2. This is an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which hydrogen or electrons are transferred from 2-oxoglutarate and one other donor, and one atom of oxygen is incorporated into each donor.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on superoxide radicals as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction (redox) reaction in which a superoxide radical (O2- or O2.-) acts as a hydrogen or electron acceptor.

label.value: oxidoreductase activity, acting on metal ions

value.value: Catalysis of an oxidation-reduction in which the oxidation state of metal ion is altered.

label.value: transferase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a group, e.g. a methyl group, glycosyl group, acyl group, phosphorus-containing, or other groups, from one compound (generally regarded as the donor) to another compound (generally regarded as the acceptor). Transferase is the systematic name for any enzyme of EC class 2.

label.value: transferase activity, transferring one-carbon groups

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a one-carbon group from one compound (donor) to another (acceptor).

label.value: hydroxymethyl-, formyl- and related transferase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a hydroxymethyl- or formyl group from one compound (donor) to another (acceptor).

label.value: carboxyl- or carbamoyltransferase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a carboxyl- or carbamoyl group from one compound (donor) to another (acceptor).

label.value: acyltransferase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of an acyl group from one compound (donor) to another (acceptor).

label.value: acyltransferase activity, transferring groups other than amino-acyl groups

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of an acyl group, other than amino-acyl, from one compound (donor) to another (acceptor).

label.value: aminoacyltransferase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of an amino-acyl group from one compound (donor) to another (acceptor).

label.value: glutathione gamma-glutamylcysteinyltransferase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the reaction: glutathione + Glu(-Cys)(n)-Gly = Gly + Glu(-Cys)(n+1)-Gly.

label.value: glycosyltransferase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a glycosyl group from one compound (donor) to another (acceptor).

label.value: hexosyltransferase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a hexosyl group from one compound (donor) to another (acceptor).

label.value: transferase activity, transferring alkyl or aryl (other than methyl) groups

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of an alkyl or aryl (but not methyl) group from one compound (donor) to another (acceptor).

label.value: transferase activity, transferring phosphorus-containing groups

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a phosphorus-containing group from one compound (donor) to another (acceptor).

definition.value: Note that this term encompasses all kinase activities, as well as activities that transfer other phosphorus-containing groups such as diphosphate or nucleotides.

label.value: phosphotransferase activity, alcohol group as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a phosphorus-containing group from one compound (donor) to an alcohol group (acceptor).

label.value: phosphotransferase activity, carboxyl group as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a phosphorus-containing group from one compound (donor) to a carboxyl group (acceptor).

label.value: phosphotransferase activity, phosphate group as acceptor

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a phosphorus-containing group from one compound (donor) to a phosphate group (acceptor).

label.value: diphosphotransferase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a diphosphate group from one compound (donor) to a another (acceptor).

label.value: nucleotidyltransferase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a nucleotidyl group to a reactant.

label.value: phosphotransferase activity, for other substituted phosphate groups

value.value: Catalysis of the transfer of a substituted phosphate group, other than diphosphate or nucleotidyl residues, from one compound (donor) to a another (acceptor).

label.value: hydrolase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the hydrolysis of various bonds, e.g. C-O, C-N, C-C, phosphoric anhydride bonds, etc.

label.value: hydrolase activity, acting on ester bonds

value.value: Catalysis of the hydrolysis of any ester bond.

label.value: phosphatase activity

value.value: Catalysis of the hydrolysis of phosphoric monoesters, releasing inorganic phosphate.

label.value: exonuclease activity, active with either ribo- or deoxyribonucleic acids and producing 5'-phosphomonoesters

value.value: Catalysis of the hydrolysis of ester linkages within nucleic acids by removing nucleotide residues from the 3' or 5' end to yield 5' phosphomonoesters.

definition.value: Note that this activity can catalyze cleavage of DNA or RNA.

label.value: hydrolase activity, acting on glycosyl bonds

value.value: Catalysis of the hydrolysis of any glycosyl bond.

label.value: hydrolase activity, hydrolyzing N-glycosyl compounds

value.value: Catalysis of the hydrolysis of any N-glycosyl bond.

label.value: hydrolase activity, acting on carbon-nitrogen (but not peptide) bonds

value.value: Catalysis of the hydrolysis of any carbon-nitrogen bond, C-N, with the exception of peptide bonds.

label.value: hydrolase activity, acting on carbon-nitrogen (but not peptide) bonds, in linear amides

value.value: Catalysis of the hydrolysis of any non-peptide carbon-nitrogen bond in a linear amide.

label.value: hydrolase activity, acting on carbon-nitrogen (but not peptide) bonds, in linear amidines

value.value: Catalysis of the hydrolysis of any non-peptide carbon-nitrogen bond in a linear amidine, a compound of the form R-C(=NH)-NH2.

label.value: hydrolase activity, acting on carbon-nitrogen (but not peptide) bonds, in cyclic amidines

value.value: Catalysis of the hydrolysis of any non-peptide carbon-nitrogen bond in a cyclic amidine, a compound of the form R-C(=NH)-NH2.

label.value: hydrolase activity, acting on acid anhydrides

value.value: Catalysis of the hydrolysis of any acid anhydride.

label.value: hydrolase activity, acting on acid anhydrides, in phosphorus-containing anhydrides

value.value: Catalysis of the hydrolysis of any acid anhydride which contains phosphorus.
